in]]||[[Hull Kingston Rovers|Hull KR]]|| 2 Years || October 2019<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hullkr.co.uk/greg-minikin-signs-for-rovers/|title=Greg Minikin signs for Hull KR on two-year deal!|date=2019-10-10|website=Hull KR|language=en-GB|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Will Maher]] || [[Hull Kingston Rovers|Hull KR]] || 2 Years || October 2019<ref>{{Cite news | url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/rugby-league/50027021 |title = Will Maher: Hull KR sign Castleford forward|work = BBC Sport|date = 12 October 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Jake Sweeting]]||[[Featherstone Rovers]]|| 1 Year || October 2019<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.seriousaboutrl.com/featherstone-sign-castleford-halfback-23747/|title=Featherstone sign Castleford halfback|date=2019-10-29|website=Serious About Rugby League|language=en-GB|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Jamie Ellis]]||[[Hull Kingston Rovers|Hull KR]]|| 1 Year || December 2019<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://castlefordtigers.com/article.php?id=6703|title=Ellis departs Tigers|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n|}\n\n== Staff ==\n\n=== Coaching staff ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Name:- !! Position:-\n|-\n| [[Daryl Powell]] || Head Coach\n|-\n| [[Danny Orr]] || Assistant Coach\n|-\n| [[Ryan Sheridan (rugby league)|Ryan Sheridan]] || Assistant Coach\n|-\n| [[Jamie Bell]] || Head of Strength & Conditioning\n|-\n| [[Matt Crowther]] || Head Physiotherapist\n|-\n| Michael Brown || Rehab Physiotherapist\n|-\n| [[Andy Lynch (rugby league)|Andy Lynch]] || Player Welfare Manager\n|}\n\n=== Youth Development ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Name:- !! Position:-\n|-\n| Pete Riding || Head of Youth Performance & Scholarship Head Coach\n|-\n| [[Tony Smith (rugby league, born 1970)|Tony Smith]] || Under 19's Head Coach\n|-\n| Darren Higgins || Talent Development Manager\n|-\n| Jamie Bell || Academy Strength & Conditioning\n|-\n| Brain Stanley || Scholarship Team Manager\n|-\n| Lee Holmes |